line_1: Or softly glide by the Canal,
line_2: And swiftly shoot along the Mall,

line_1: And shadows in disguise skate o'er the iced Canal;
line_2: Here spirit-beaux flutter along the Mall,

line_1: Extends the view, and spreads the smooth canal,
line_2: In vain thy Lord commands the streams to fall,

line_1: As circles on a smooth canal;
line_2: Wide and wider spreads the vale;
